		<descript>
			<abstract>The data displays the geographic boundary of the Apalachicola National Estuarine Research Reserve (ANERR).  The polygon was created using on screen digitization from correlating paper maps against 1 meter DOQQ's.  A graphic representing the boundary limits are in the Apalachicola NERR management plan.</abstract>
			<purpose>The data provides display quality graphics representing the ANERR.</purpose>
